title: Hold your horses, Bob! - 1st single
description:
This is the first release from the small indie company MakeMyDayMusic in Sweden and it contains the debut single "Do what you like (but don&#039;t do it here)" with the music collective "Hold your horses, Bob!". The title is said to be a Springsteen quote, but the music is not Springsteenish whatsoever. Rather some experimental Beck Hansen-like rock.

1. Blues for a hip king (mp3@192 kbit/s)
2. Peace is a state of mind (mp3@192 kbit/s)
3. Put a peephole in my brain (mp3@192 kbit/s)

Spread it around, if this is their debut they&#039;re bound for some good releases in the future.
